text: Jenő Hégner-Tóth (April 17, 1894 – June 10, 1915) was a Hungarian water polo player who competed in the 1912 Summer Olympics. He was part of the Hungarian team in the 1912 tournament. He died in Hommona. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1915 deaths Category:Hungarian male water polo players Category:Olympic water polo players of Hungary Category:Water polo players at the 1912 Summer Olympics
